name: Dash
description: Thomas Geiger developed a new NFT edition called "I want to become a millionaire - Crypto Market" with 15 Logo-Gifs, that take reference from the current frontrunners of the Crypto market. Staying in line with the pricing model from "The great Stock exchange", all NFTs will be aligned with their cryptocurrency share prices on the market. Since this is constantly fluctuating, the corresponding rate may change as well. Besides the digital signature, each piece is signed and numbered by hand.
